COMMENT @%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%

MACRO:		rndwwbf

DESCRIPTION:	Round a WWFixed value to a WBFixed

ARGUMENTS:
	source - A WWFixed value to round

%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%@

rndwwbf	macro	source
	local	round, done, drf, dri, regargs

regargs	= 0
